From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: user <user@localhost>
Date: Thu, 13 Mar 2026 14:30:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] device: TouchKeypad init triggers and sepolicy

Adds init property triggers that write to /sys/devices/touch_keypad/turn_off
when persist.vendor.touchkeypad.disabled changes. Includes SELinux policy
for vendor_touchkeypad_prop, sysfs labeling, and ueventd permissions.

